SQLite DATABASE:
    Database name  = Movies
    Table name = MOVIE
    Attributes/Column name = ID,NAME,ACTOR,ACTRESS,DIRECTOR,YEAR

PROCEDURE:
    1) Sqlite.py --> Table is created
    2) SqLiteInsertion.py --> Records are inserted into the table MOVIE
    3) SqLiteSelection.py --> Records are display using SELECT Query
    4) SqLiteSelectionWithParameter.py --> Selection performed based on condition (To display the movie details released in the year 2022)
    5) SqLiteSelectionBaedOnActor.py --> Selection performed based on actor name ( To display movie details when Actor name is Dulquer Salmaan)